---
import SiteNav from './SiteNav.astro';
---

<header class="landing-hero" data-theme="hero">
  <SiteNav />
  <div class="[ wrapper ] [ flow ] hero-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Solutions</p>
    <h1>Infrastructure for the open science ecosystem<em>.</em></h1>
    <p>The greatest untapped potential lies in the connections between the different parts of the scholarly publishing ecosystem. By creating interoperable, open-source tools we can enable communities to work together in ways that weren't previously possible.</p>
    <p>Our development of open infrastructure lies in co-publishing. By prioritising consistent management and interoperability we facilitate existing open publishing and pave the way for high quality, performance-driven solutions for the publishing community.</p>
    <figure>
      <img src="/images/solutions-placeholder.png" alt="" />
    </figure>
  </div>
</header>
